data.description: ***Ask about the Assumable VA loan @ 4.75%. This home provides the warm, cozy feel from the moment you walk through the front door. It does have several wow factors, such as the beautiful fireplace, spacious kitchen/dining/family room setup, and the bonus room that is large enough to provide many use options.  Large island in the kitchen, convenient half bath on the main floor, New sod in the front yard, fenced yard, and wired for a hot tub.
